		<Row Tag="LOC_ZYL_RVC_MAP_NAME" Language="en_US"><Text>Rich Vertical Continent (Repaired)</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_ZYL_RVC_MAP_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US"><Text>A resource-rich vertical continent with broad eastern and western seas. Defaults to east-west team spawns. Integrated from Team PVP Rich Vertical Continent with repaired map sizes, generation, and localization.</Text></Row>
