		<Row Tag="LOC_ZYL_RVC_TEAM_RANDOM" Language="en_US"><Text>Random</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_ZYL_RVC_TEAM_RANDOM_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US"><Text>Uses standard continent stamping and unrestricted spawn directions.</Text></Row>
