		<Row Tag="LOC_ZYL_RVC_CITY_STATE_PLACEMENT_NAME" Language="en_US"><Text>City-State Placement Rules</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_ZYL_RVC_CITY_STATE_PLACEMENT_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US"><Text>Selects the spacing and fallback rules used to place city-states. Major-civilization placement is unchanged.</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_ZYL_RVC_CITY_STATE_PLACEMENT_SINGLE" Language="en_US"><Text>Single Player</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_ZYL_RVC_CITY_STATE_PLACEMENT_SINGLE_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US"><Text>Uses the standard Firaxis city-state spacing and fallback behavior.</Text></Row>
