		<Row Tag="LOC_ZYL_RVC_CITY_STATE_PLACEMENT_MULTI_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US"><Text>Preserves the map's stricter Team PVP city-state spacing and removal rules.</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_ZYL_RVC_SPAWN_RECALCULATION_NAME" Language="en_US"><Text>Balanced Spawn Recalculation</Text></Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_ZYL_RVC_SPAWN_RECALCULATION_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US"><Text>Uses the integrated BBS-derived starting-position allocator and retries unsuitable layouts.</Text></Row>

